{"tid":1534254,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【一國一制】後香港社會實況","createTime":"2019-09-03T02:58:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T03:04:43.000Z","uid":44914,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"14d0e80a983aa8af119e50eba69df7fb00b14ad7","tid":1534254,"uid":44914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:58:06.000Z","msg":"如果今次輸左 行一國一制/假一國兩制既後香港社會會有：<br />\n新屋嶺集中營<br />\n警犬子弟貴族學校 (大/中/小)<br />\n設立速龍英勇徽章<br />\n討論區實名制<br />\n辱警罪 (問你良心去左邊都算)<br />\n國歌法 (被站立 包括輪椅人士)<br />\n以言入罪法<br />\n督灰減刑/步步高昇制<br />\n燈柱實時監控市民系統<br />\n香港信用評級<br />\n每人每日提款上限<br />\n豬肉配給制<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"680624af928d062a0fcac31702cb36a9fd95f3f8","tid":1534254,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:58:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月8！到時見！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e04e2d8700328db4627ba5b847f7ad800eecede3","tid":1534254,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:58:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我唔想知佢錄音內容<br />\n我推到同溫層既大家知道<br />\n你地負責幫手去fb啊等等宣傳得唔得<br />\n唔好再理膠post喇 關注返行動post<br />\n再好好運用6月至今每個核彈去twitter做文宣喇<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFCbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=1f610d65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，<br />\n請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n-大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n-高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n-高舉大量國旗<br />\n-唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼 補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n-領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n<br />\n無人申請不反 908都要照上街<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"94fbe2a05b7f0ee21f79921af9e3ead99a0db253","tid":1534254,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:00:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">出糧換美金  全民提款日</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.07 機場交通測試 13 00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.08 美國人權及民主法案大遊行</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.13 各區同慶賀中秋 人鏈 19:00 - 22:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.14 機場交通測試 13 00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">轉頭見</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></div>"},{"pid":"24a9fb4c32f8ad119ff2e09bdcd7b42af29acf34","tid":1534254,"uid":44914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:01:41.000Z","msg":"721 831"},{"pid":"a0c165c982ffeaf7d79035314e8690a9dbe694b3","tid":1534254,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:04:43.000Z","msg":"強制大灣區"}]}